Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.25,0:00:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood pressure, 120 over 80;\Npulse, 92.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.72,0:00:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I will now remove the bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.70,0:00:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I have removed the bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.74,0:00:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The removal is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.51,0:00:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little early to be relieved;
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.05,0:00:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,we must still reinforce the walls\Nof the damaged blood vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.92,0:00:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.02,0:00:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the proline ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.25,0:00:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:24.20,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,0)\pos(360,340)}Downfall
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood pressure, 128 over 72;\Npulse, 88.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.66,0:02:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems the anesthesia is still working.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best to survive...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Dr. Boyer...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like yours went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The surgery did...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The mayor died.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.23,0:03:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is that so?\NThat's a shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph! You act as though\Nit's none of your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.44,0:03:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the very one\Nwho abandoned our team
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,just before surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... but, that child\Nwas brought in before the mayor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it matter, who was first?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is, because you selfishly\Npulled out of our team,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,we were forced to try to fill\Nthe vacuum you created!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But... Listen to me! I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You upset the teamwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,By order of the Director,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I instructed you\Nto perform the surgery...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,on the mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.13,0:03:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But you... You ignored me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,B-but, Chief, at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The success of a surgery\Ndepends upon trust
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.47,0:03:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,among the entire staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But you made a grand stand play!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:04:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have already reported this\Nto the Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.35,0:04:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He greatly regrets this incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.02,0:04:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,which has lowered\Nthe prestige of this hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait a minute!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,At present, that child's blood pressure\Nis 114 over 82; pulse, 84.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,His vitals are very stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...\NThat's good...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... That operation...\NIt was wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mayor Roddecker, who collapsed\Nwhile on holiday,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.63,0:04:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}has passed away at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Upon hearing this unexpected news,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.47,0:04:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}people have been arriving\Nat the Mayor's office
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:04:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with bouquets of flowers,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}many reminiscing on\Nthe life of the Mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A press conference has just been held\Nat Eisler Memorial Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}where the Mayor was taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The cause of\NMayor Roddecker's death
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was due to a cerebral infarction\Nstemming from
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a severe emphraxis\Nof the inner carotid artery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We did everything we could for him,\Nbut it caused severe brain swelling,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.66,0:05:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,which resulted in\Nthis unfortunate outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.93,0:05:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As for naming a successor,\Na city official explained that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}concrete steps will be taken
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- as soon as possible.\N{\i0}- I've got to get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the case of the murder of\NMr. and Mrs. Liebert late last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Judging from the signs of\Na search in the rooms,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.91,0:05:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}police believe\Nthis may have been a robbery...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.31,0:05:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or perhaps the act of\Na political terrorist
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}against this couple\Nwho had fled here from their country.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A two-pronged investigation\Nis under way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of this couple's twin children, the son,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}who received a gunshot wound\Nto the head
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}underwent successful surgery, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:06:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}has still to regain consciousness.\NHe is listed in critical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, for the weather...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The whole country is
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- in for clear weather...\N{\i0}- That boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what will happen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Reinhardt in ICU\Nis complaining that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,she just can't sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we give her something\Nto help her sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.09,0:06:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma, are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh... in that case,\Ngive her one Halcyon tablet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That man! He's been unfocused\Nall day long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Becker!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.35,0:06:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems you've had a trying time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Has the Director\Nhanded down his judgment?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:06:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I warned you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.13,0:07:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you the hospital\Nis ruled by politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you played your cards right,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,your future would have been\Nsmooth sailing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I guess this means you and I\Nare in the same boat now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, don't be so depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get a chance\Nto redeem your reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go have some drinks.\NIt'll cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I still need to get a statement\Nfrom the girl twin...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't discuss that with you now,\NDetective!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.47,0:07:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl is gone from her room!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl is always\Nslipping out of her room
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and wandering through the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.93,0:08:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.77,0:08:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Eisler Memorial Hospital has\Nproven to be
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the nation's leading medical facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.35,0:08:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That is first and foremost,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the result of our being blessed with
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,such excellent personnel\Nsuch as you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sincerely grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,unfortunately, the Mayor died\Nhere in this hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But, as always,\Nwe had done our utmost to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The public's evaluation of this hospital\Nhas not changed one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a round of applause\Nfor Dr. Boyer and Dr. Eisen,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,who strived to the end\Nto save the Mayor's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.56,0:09:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at your paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you will continue to\Nwork on your research.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Director Heinemann!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I must apologize\Nfor my actions...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now... What's done is done.\NDirector?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.05,0:09:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You did what you thought you should.\NLet's leave it at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.93,0:09:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Director...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,let's have a word from\Nthe Head of Neurosurgery!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me... I'm being called up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.57,0:10:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.61,0:10:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the newly appointed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Boyer, please...\NPlease come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, what is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wish to remain at this hospital,\Nyou may do so,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but you'd better give up the idea of\Nrising any further as a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be impossible for\Nsomeone with a flawed character
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,such as yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll recognize your skill as a surgeon,\Nbut that is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.53,0:10:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You should also give up any ideas of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,presenting any papers\Nat future conferences.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But, sir... Please listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you wish to move\Nto another hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.48,0:10:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of\Nwriting you a recommendation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This means it's no use for you\Nto have any ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You may consider your path\Nto becoming
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the doctor you envisioned closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Surgery requires teamwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Only with the help of each\Nand every one of you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,can a life be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva, won't you talk to your father\Nfor me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't done anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I just operated on\Nan emergency case
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,in the order in which\Nhe was brought in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... your engagement ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.66,0:12:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.06,0:12:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, Dr. Norden,\Ndon't you look elegant?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,As do you! You're more beautiful\Nthan ever tonight, Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.27,0:12:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What a laugh, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,After coming across\NDirector Heinemann's paper,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here to Germany,\Nand he made me what I am today...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose that paper\Nthat I was so impressed by
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.78,0:12:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,was probably written for him\Nby someone somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that he was using me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,but I believed,\Nwhen I reached a certain position,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be able to work on research\Nof my choice to my heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.67,0:13:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are scholars, first and foremost.\NIsn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not right! Saving people's lives\Nis what's most important to a doctor!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all, people's lives\Naren't created equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no distinction\Nbetween people's lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You say there's a flaw\Nin my character?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.55,0:13:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You call yourself a doctor;\Nbut you're just money hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard... That bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's better off dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.77,0:13:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have you to thank...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.44,0:13:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You opened my eyes, as a doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:13:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You must do your best to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.85,0:14:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I threw everything away\Nin order to operate on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how far I went\Nin order to bring you back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You know your name, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name is Anna Liebert,\Nisn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, didn't I, Detective?\NIt's too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't anything be done, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, she saw her parents\Nshot to death before her very eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:15:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She has no physical wounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but extreme trauma seems to have\Nbrought on amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.18,0:15:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please refrain from
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to get a statement from her\Nfor a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a difficult case, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The victim was\Nan East German diplomat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't solve this quickly,\Nthe BKA will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Those guys always come
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.86,0:15:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and steal the thunder from\Nus state police!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't got the time to take it slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... What if we do this?\NWe let her see her brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be relieved to see him\Nand her memory might return.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.61,0:15:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot agree on such a gamble-\None suggested by an amateur, at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Dr. Tenma\Nwill probably not permit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.82,0:15:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the doctor\Nin charge of her brother Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk... What the heck\Nam I supposed to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:16:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be in a daze.\NYou look awfully tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.47,0:16:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been so busy\Nwith emergency surgeries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They've been working you\Nto the bone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,ever since you were\Ndemoted from Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.\NIt actually makes me feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now... Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I've just been paged.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.99,0:16:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so tired,\Nbut you still have work to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.89,0:16:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The more diligent you are,\Nthe worse it'll be for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.23,0:16:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this, Director Heinemann...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,See all the gifts\Nand letters of encouragement.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There are mountains of them\Nin his sister's room, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,After losing their parents\Nthese two only have each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The mass media keeps reporting on\Ntheir heartbreaking plight,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and this is the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as this hospital is concerned,\Nthey're nothing but an inconvenience;
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.18,0:16:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,what with no sign of anyone paying\Ntheir medical expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.12,0:16:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So their story is a pitiful one-\Nthat's just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.79,0:16:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:17:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That means this hospital is\Ngarnering attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.06,0:17:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,For that reason alone,\Nthese kids are valuable...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.37,0:17:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll give the media\Na photo of the siblings together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the media keeps asking\Nfor something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it. It'll be a picture\Nof the orphaned siblings
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,trying their best to live\Nwithin the warmhearted care
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,of our hospital's staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But the boy's doctor says\Nit is still too early
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.89,0:17:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,to allow them to see each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's on his case?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.63,0:17:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dismiss him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no need to give that man\Na position that gets so much attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.61,0:17:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Take Dr. Tenma off the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a heartwarming gift\Nfrom the citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:17:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:17:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel, Mrs. Hankel?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, I feel quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.10,0:18:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Your stitches will be removed soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so it won't be long\Nuntil you're released.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be able to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but as I said, you must rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Give Mrs. Hankel regular doses
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,of an anticonvulsant\Nand a hypotensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.46,0:18:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.83,0:18:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They let her see her brother.\NThen she gave a loud scream and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.87,0:18:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you bring them together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.15,0:19:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Take her back to her room, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.75,0:19:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Boyer, what is the meaning of this?\NWhy the camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... We're going to give the media
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.99,0:19:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,a picture of the emotional meeting\Nof the two children.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.60,0:19:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Who allowed you to do such a thing?\NI am the boy's doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You have been dismissed\Nas Johan's doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,As of today, he is my patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.67,0:19:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided that it would be fine\Nto let them see each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Those children...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make those children fodder\Nfor the media!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it by order of the Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it would be best for you\Nnot to fight it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who saved this boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a duty to protect him\Nuntil he is completely healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.86,0:19:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case,\Ntake a look at the boy's reaction!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as he saw his sister,\Nhe extended his hand and cried tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He regained consciousness\Nand showed a normal reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That means the surgery\Nwas a great success.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job. Your work is done now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back to where you belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...\NDon't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares what the Director says?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.74,0:20:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares what the Chief says?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all money and power hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.66,0:20:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I am not wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home, Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Father? Are you in your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief?\NAre you still in a meeting at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.55,0:21:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, are you asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.99,0:21:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.31,0:22:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard... He's better off dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.07,0:23:53.49,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,0)\pos(360,340)}A Murder

